#include <iostream>
#include <stdio.h>
#include <vector>
#include <iterator>

using namespace std;

int main() {
	
	int v, n, i, j, flag, t;
	vector<int> A;
	
	while( scanf("%d", &v ) > 0 )
		A.push_back( v );
	n = A.size();	
	
	for( i = 0;i < n;i++ ) {
		flag = 0;
		for( j = 0;j < ( n - i - 1 );j++ ) {
			
			if( A[ j ] > A[ j + 1 ] ) {
				flag = 1;
				t = A[ j ];
				A[ j ] = A[ j + 1 ];
				A[ j + 1 ] = t;
			}
		}
		if( flag ) {
			
			copy( A.begin(), A.end(), ostream_iterator<int> ( cout," " ) );
			cout << endl;			
		}
	}
	
	return 0;
}
